<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Payment Issue - VivaExcel Blog</title>
  <!--[if mso]>
  <noscript>
    <xml>
      <o:OfficeDocumentSettings>
        <o:PixelsPerInch>96</o:PixelsPerInch>
      </o:OfficeDocumentSettings>
    </xml>
  </noscript>
  <![endif]-->
</head>
<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333333; background-color: #f4f6f9;">
  <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="background-color: #f4f6f9;">
    <tr>
      <td align="center" style="padding: 40px 20px;">
        <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="600" style="max-width: 600px; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.07);">
          <!-- Header -->
          <tr>
            <td style="background-color: #1E4DB7; padding: 24px 40px; text-align: center;">
              <h1 style="margin: 0; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; color: #ffffff;">VivaExcel Blog</h1>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <!-- Body -->
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 40px;">
              <!-- Warning Icon -->
              <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="margin: 0 0 24px;">
                <tr>
                  <td align="center">
                    <div style="display: inline-block; background-color: #fef2f2; border: 2px solid #ef4444; border-radius: 50%; width: 64px; height: 64px; line-height: 64px; text-align: center; font-size: 32px; color: #ef4444;">
                      !
                    </div>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>

              <h2 style="margin: 0 0 20px; font-size: 22px; color: #1a1a2e; text-align: center;">We couldn't process your payment</h2>

              <p style="margin: 0 0 16px; color: #4b5563; font-size: 16px;">Hello {{name}},</p>

              <p style="margin: 0 0 16px; color: #4b5563; font-size: 16px;">We attempted to charge your payment method for your VivaExcel Blog subscription, but the transaction was unsuccessful.</p>

              <!-- Alert Box -->
              <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="margin: 24px 0;">
                <tr>
                  <td style="background-color: #fef2f2; border-left: 4px solid #ef4444; padding: 16px 20px; border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;">
                    <p style="margin: 0 0 8px; color: #991b1b; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600;">Action Required</p>
                    <p style="margin: 0; color: #7f1d1d; font-size: 14px;">Please update your payment information to continue accessing premium content without interruption.</p>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>

              <!-- Common Reasons -->
              <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="background-color: #f8f9fb; border-radius: 8px; margin: 24px 0;">
                <tr>
                  <td style="padding: 24px;">
                    <h3 style="margin: 0 0 12px; font-size: 15px; color: #1a1a2e;">Common reasons for payment failure:</h3>
                    <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%">
                      <tr><td style="padding: 4px 0; color: #4b5563; font-size: 14px;">&#8226; Expired credit or debit card</td></tr>
                      <tr><td style="padding: 4px 0; color: #4b5563; font-size: 14px;">&#8226; Insufficient funds</td></tr>
                      <tr><td style="padding: 4px 0; color: #4b5563; font-size: 14px;">&#8226; Card issuer declined the transaction</td></tr>
                      <tr><td style="padding: 4px 0; color: #4b5563; font-size: 14px;">&#8226; Updated card number or security code</td></tr>
                    </table>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>

              <!-- CTA Button -->
              <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="margin: 32px 0;">
                <tr>
                  <td align="center">
                    <a href="{{billingUrl}}" style="display: inline-block; background-color: #ef4444; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; padding: 14px 40px; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px;">Update Payment Method</a>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>

              <p style="margin: 0 0 8px; color: #9ca3af; font-size: 13px;">If the button above doesn't work, copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
              <p style="margin: 0 0 24px; word-break: break-all;"><a href="{{billingUrl}}" style="color: #1E4DB7; font-size: 12px;">{{billingUrl}}</a></p>

              <!-- Info Box -->
              <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="margin: 24px 0;">
                <tr>
                  <td style="background-color: #eff6ff; border-left: 4px solid #1E4DB7; padding: 16px 20px; border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;">
                    <p style="margin: 0; color: #1e3a5f; font-size: 14px;"><strong>Note:</strong> We'll automatically retry the payment in a few days. If the issue persists, your subscription may be paused until payment is resolved.</p>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>

              <p style="margin: 24px 0 8px; color: #4b5563; font-size: 14px;">Need help? Our support team is here to assist you.</p>
              <p style="margin: 0; color: #1a1a2e; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600;">The VivaExcel Blog Team</p>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <!-- Footer -->
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 24px 40px; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; text-align: center;">
              <p style="margin: 0 0 8px; color: #9ca3af; font-size: 12px;">&copy; {{year}} VivaExcel Blog. All rights reserved.</p>
              <p style="margin: 0; color: #9ca3af; font-size: 12px;">Questions? Contact us at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}" style="color: #1E4DB7; text-decoration: none;">{{supportEmail}}</a></p>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>
